%% CCB Agentic Loop Workflow — lifecycle, feedback, and recovery
%% This is a protocol view. Solid arrows are requests or evidence; the Controller remains program authority.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 用户
    participant FD as Frontdesk
    participant P as Planner
    participant C as 程序控制脊柱<br/>Controller / Loop Runner
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant D as Task Detailer
    participant T as Topology
    participant W as Worker
    participant R as Reviewer
    participant G as Git + Root Verification
    participant RR as Round Reviewer

    User->>FD: 项目请求
    FD->>P: ask --silence：完整 Intake / Blocked Evidence
    P->>C: 导入 task 或 task-set；写入 revision-fenced authority
    C->>O: 激活 Orchestrator triage，提供 Planner macro packet

    alt direct_execution
        O->>C: direct_execution route；进入确定性 physical dispatch
    else needs_detail（仅此时激活 Detailer）
        O->>D: needs_detail；提供 refinement request 与 Planner refs
        alt local_detail_ready
            D->>O: 返回局部 detail packet
        else macro impact / planner_replan_required
            D->>P: 受限 silent ask：replan envelope
            P->>C: 接受修订；旧 bundle 作废、阻止 Worker dispatch
            C->>O: 新鲜 activation，重新编排
        else needs_clarification
            D->>FD: 提供澄清请求证据
            FD->>User: 转达澄清问题
            User->>FD: 提供答复
            FD->>D: 转达答复证据，继续局部细化
        else blocked
            D->>C: 可验证的阻塞证据
            C->>FD: 保留权威状态；仅不可恢复时升级
        end
    else macro_adjustment_request
        O->>P: macro artifact；请求 Planner-owned 更新
        P->>C: 接受修订；旧 bundle 作废
        C->>O: 新鲜 activation，重新 triage
    else blocked
        O->>C: blocker evidence
        C->>FD: 保留权威状态；仅不可恢复时升级
    end

    opt 已取得可派发的 direct_execution 或 local detail
        O->>C: 语义 bundle：nodes、依赖、logical roles、验收、rework policy
    end
    C->>T: 校验 schema / capacity / revision / digest，提交 mount intent
    T-->>C: 具体绑定、已观察的就绪状态

    loop 每个 DAG-ready workgroup（1–4 个槽位，可同时打开）
        C->>W: 仅一次 root Worker ask；绑定 worktree digest
        W->>R: restricted ask --chain 到指定 Reviewer
        alt pass
            R-->>W: status: pass
        else rework_required（有界）
            R-->>W: status: rework_required
            W->>W: 修复后仅向同一 Reviewer 再次 chain
            W->>R: restricted ask --chain
            R-->>W: terminal verdict
        else blocked / non_converged
            R-->>W: non-pass terminal verdict
        end
        W-->>C: 最终 node result 与已绑定 tree 证据
    end

    C->>G: 确定性 Git integration + root verification
    G->>RR: 轮次证据
    RR-->>C: round gate 结果
    C->>C: 导入 child authority；释放或 busy-retain，并记录 residue

    alt task-set 达到稳定闭合条件
        C->>C: aggregate child outcomes；生成 closure intent（exact-once）
        C->>P: silent Planner backfill（revision-fenced closure envelope）
        P->>C: Brief / Roadmap / TODO proposal
        C->>FD: 校验并提交 Frontdesk status
        FD->>User: 最终报告
    else replan_required
        C->>P: 一份聚合 replan 输入；不按 child 重复 ask
    else partial / blocked
        C->>P: 记录已落地范围、剩余工作或阻塞证据
        P->>FD: 需要时给出用户可见状态
    end

    opt 重启 / submit-persist-start 故障恢复
        C->>C: 从 transaction journal、intent、job lineage、digest 与 revision 恢复
        Note over C: 同 identity + digest 复用；冲突复用 fail closed；不从 provider prose 推断成功
    end
